org.flowvisor.flows

Class FederatedFlowMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.flowvisor.flows.FederatedFlowMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, FlowMap

    public class FederatedFlowMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements FlowMap, java.lang.Cloneable
    Author:
    ash Implements FlowMap, in a federated fashion. Each field of the flow entry is indexed in its own data structure. This data structure is either a trie or a hashmap depending on the type of the field.
    See Also:
    for more detail.
